Message:
Just you wait, Master!
I’m coming after you~!
...Gotcha!

Nnnrrrgh...
Why are you rubbing
your cheeks against mine?
Aren’t you being clingier
than usual today, Master?

No, I’m okay with that.
I love it when Master
gives me hugs too, after all.

Alright, this time...
I’m also gonna squeeeeeze
my cheeks against yours.

When our cheeks touch
each other, they say hello~♪

Hehehe, this is sooo much fun~
...? Who’s that poking me
from behind...?

Huh, Master?!
But, aren’t you
also in front of me...?

Huh? Wh-What?!
Master...why’s there
so many of you?!
